*And many others - each logo belongs to its respective company/project*

## Removal Requests

If you are a trademark owner and would like your logo removed, please:

1. Open an issue in this repository
2. Email the project maintainers
3. We will promptly remove the logo and replace it with a generic placeholder

## Alternative Sources

Many of these logos were sourced from:

- Official company websites and press kits
- Public brand guidelines and media resources  
- Open source repositories with appropriate licenses
- Vector logo collections (with attribution where required)

## No Endorsement

The inclusion of these logos does not imply endorsement by the respective companies of this project, nor does it imply endorsement by this project of the respective products or services.